WEAPON

Name: Hoof spikes
Identified by: b_example
Description:
Some mean looking horse-shoes with thick spikes pointing outwards.

Type: hoof melee

Damage roll: 1d5

Damage type: Piercing. 

Critical misses:
The hoof spike gets stuck in your enemy! You struggle to rip it out. : Can't move for 1 turn.
    :You rip the spike out of your enemy!
You stumble onto your muzzle as you miss your target. : 1d3 dmg to self.

Critical hits + effect:
Your hoof spike smashes into the %enemy%'s eye. It looks painful. : 2d5 dmg. Enemy can't move for 1 turn. Blind enemy.

